title: Alpha Hunter
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Broods of [[Raveners]] treat the [[Red Terror]] as though it were an [[Independent Character]]. In addition, when a brood of [[Raveners]] containing the [[Red Terror]] charges, the whole unit gains the [[Rage]] special rule.